{"tid":1813022,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國宣布管制AI軟體出口，防範中國等競爭對手取得敏感技術","createTime":"2020-01-06T03:13:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-09T00:44:49.000Z","uid":141151,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c8e43e10f90dc69230c07b08722922e4d5d08f8f","tid":1813022,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T03:13:19.000Z","msg":"美國宣布管制AI軟體出口，防範中國等競爭對手取得敏感技術<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%94%A2%E7%B6%93-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E7%AE%A1%E5%88%B6ai%E8%BB%9F%E9%AB%94%E5%87%BA%E5%8F%A3-%E9%98%B2%E7%AF%84%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%AD%89%E7%AB%B6%E7%88%AD%E5%B0%8D%E6%89%8B%E5%8F%96%E5%BE%97%E6%95%8F%E6%84%9F%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93-000531360.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.stock.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%2594%25A2%25E7%25B6%2593-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E5%25B8%2583%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E5%2588%25B6ai%25E8%25BB%259F%25E9%25AB%2594%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%258F%25A3-%25E9%2598%25B2%25E7%25AF%2584%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25AD%2589%25E7%25AB%25B6%25E7%2588%25AD%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%2589%258B%25E5%258F%2596%25E5%25BE%2597%25E6%2595%258F%25E6%2584%259F%25E6%258A%2580%25E8%25A1%2593-000531360.html&d=bwUHcV0Pscj1NrVo4Cy%2FDZUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=2e27ca8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%94%A2%E7%B6%93-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E7%AE%A1%E5%88%B6ai%E8%BB%9F%E9%AB%94%E5%87%BA%E5%8F%A3-%E9%98%B2%E7%AF%84%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%AD%89%E7%AB%B6%E7%88%AD%E5%B0%8D%E6%89%8B%E5%8F%96%E5%BE%97%E6%95%8F%E6%84%9F%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93-000531360.html</a><br />\n<br />\n【財訊快報／陳孟朔】外電報導，美國商務部3日宣布限制人工智慧(AI)軟體出口，盼降低包括中國在內的競爭對手取得相關敏感技術。<br />\n<br />\n  根據週一(1月6日)生效的新措施，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">任何公司要從美國出口地理空間圖像軟體時，須先獲得商務部批准，出口目的地為加拿大則排除在外。雖然新規定目前只在美國生效，但華府可能稍後向其他國際機構提議在全球範圍實施。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n  美國智庫戰略與國際研究中心(CSIS)副總裁路易斯(James Lewis)指出，華府希望阻止美企幫助中國發展對軍事有利的技術，因AI軟體可幫助感應器、無人機和衛星等工具辨識目標。他強調，新措施較預期寬鬆，相信對美企海外銷售業務打擊沒想像中大。"},{"pid":"558e02bfd7a457bfbb93ff705fd711bf58fa75ef","tid":1813022,"uid":29702,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T03:20:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e20d5cfc8a66f3b723483119f1b83ca988d00260","tid":1813022,"uid":310461,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T03:21:28.000Z","msg":"Maybe part of top notch facial recognition technology in China was originated or sourced from USA."},{"pid":"5d7b8fca95f4e8c355bdf63ef5bde3fd0d6961fd","tid":1813022,"uid":98317,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T03:23:43.000Z","msg":"如果Google同Facebook  冇open source 到Tensorflow 同pytorch 支那啲AI技術點會發展得咁快....   美國其實係自己攞嚟衰..<br />\n你限制軟件出口有撚用咩，最核心既技術都比人拎左嚟用"},{"pid":"33b367c14aef52b9029fea9818b3b4869351fad9","tid":1813022,"uid":92188,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T03:28:56.000Z","msg":"加拿大都可以轉俾中國，睇實啲加拿大好"},{"pid":"fe6b20357669bdf7ec27fee6a81267c7e40a8c58","tid":1813022,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T04:42:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df636b3f6a07a0c0cbd2b2ddaeb558bf4d5dd124","tid":1813022,"uid":293557,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T04:44:19.000Z","msg":"坐等支那大背刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"625442f9c64a2aafb7946e722bb69db0079838ac","tid":1813022,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T04:48:29.000Z","msg":"Google 近一年賣左好多技術俾支那，其中一個好似電影未來報告咁，用生活行為推測佢係咪準備犯法（反共）。"},{"pid":"e3239915c927279f129431705d1b2dc4aca2b16c","tid":1813022,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"558e02bfd7a